These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, documentary, time-travel, mirindaing
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, photographer, scientist, writer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, davidoff, chaman, bolivar
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, 7up, soy-milk
1. the photographer is the person watching family movies##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the chaman-smoker is the designer##1
4. the person watching mirindaing movies is on the right of the photographer##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
6. the prince-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
7. the photographer is the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person watching mirindaing movies is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre         | family  | mirindaing  | documentary | time-travel |
| Job           | photographer | designer | writer  | scientist  |
| Cigar   | bolivar       | chaman      | prince | davidoff      |
| Beverage           | almond-milk          | mirinda     | 7up    | soy-milk     |

