.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, tram, jet-ski
City: london, hamburg, nizza, marseilles
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, baking, reading, photography
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, volleyball, water-polo
1. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is reading##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person driving the car##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Transport      | tram     | bus       | car | jet-ski        |
| City          | marseilles     | hamburg       | nizza   | london   |
| Hobby   | reading      | baking       | photography     | sudoku    |
| Sport         | volleyball | water-polo | baseball | ice-hockey |

