.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, bus, jet-ski, helicopter
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, card-games, photography, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, musical, scientific
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, light-blue, ivory, blood-red
 1. the person driving the helicopter is the person who likes blood-red##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Transport      | bus | snowmobile       | helicopter        | jet-ski        |
| Hobby           | card-games   | photography | video-games   | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | horror    | scientific | musical        |
| Color           | ivory         | pink  | blood-red       | light-blue         |

