.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, firefighter, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, animation, adventure
4 different games are played: monopoly, chess, whist, backgammon
House: farmhouse, cottage, palace, tower
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the firefighter is on the right of the tower house##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
4. the scientist is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the scientist is on the right of the bartender##1
8. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
9. the palace house is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Job           | engineer   | bartender  | scientist | firefighter |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | adventure       | mystery       | fantasy     |
| Game   | whist       | backgammon    | chess     | monopoly  |
| House           | cottage     | palace | tower     | farmhouse         |

