.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, onion, eggplant, pepper
House: gothic-revival, colonial, farmhouse, victorian
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indian, thai, turkish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, december, november
1. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
4. the indian is on the left of the french##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is the thai##1
7. the french is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
8. the person eating onion is on the right of the colonial house##1
9. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Food           | watermelon  | eggplant    | onion | pepper |
| House   | farmhouse      | colonial    | gothic-revival         | victorian    |
| Nationality   | indian   | french     | thai          | turkish      |
| Birthday         | october | june | november      | december      |

