The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, water-polo, snowboarding
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, scientific, thriller
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, amaryllis, zinnia
 1. the wooden house is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the art-deco house is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is the art-deco house##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the wooden house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| House          | art-deco  | craftsman | wooden     | gothic-revival |
| Sport           | water-polo  | snowboarding      | climbing | cricket    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific  | fantasy    | thriller  |
| Flower           | amaryllis   | zinnia       | bellflower       | balloon-flower      |

