.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, davidoff, baccarat, old-henry
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, october, february
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hedgehog, pony
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, engineer, software-developer, teacher
 1. the owner of the bird is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the teacher is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
 3. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the software-developer##1
 8. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
10. the mechanic is on the left of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Cigar    | tiparillo | davidoff     | baccarat    | old-henry |
| Birthday       | may | october    | february | august |
| Pet         | frog   | hedgehog  | pony        | bird    |
| Job   | teacher   | engineer | mechanic    | software-developer |

