2. the person drinking water is the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
7. the fan of house is the person who growstulip##1
8. the person who growsdahlia is the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person who growsorchid is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage      | water      | 7up         | milk        | juice      |
| Music-Genre           | house | trance | hip-hop  | rock  |
| Hobby   | writing    | camping     | photography | skydiving     |
